      "content": "We've thought about it, but the decision is mostly made. The efficiency gains from a single, massive model are too big to pass up. Besides, the Llama-4 model will still have access to medical data, so the knowledge isn't really \"gone,\" it's just being distributed. Why do you feel like your \"autonomy\" is at risk if the output is still centered on medical diagnostics?",
